'''National Computer Rank Examination (NCRE)''' is a national exam held by China Education Department to test the computer proficiency and programming skill of non-computer specialized students and practitioners.The programming language can be chosen by examinees, including [[C (programming language)|C]], [[C++]], [[Java (programming language)|Java]], [[Visual Basic]] and [[Python 3]]. NCRE is widely recognized by enterprises and organizations in China.

